script = ExtResource("1")
id = "rock_bottom"
display_name = "The Tweaker"
title = "Rock Bottom"
blurb = "You live behind the gas station. You know which dumpsters are good. You are, in a very specific way, free.

+ Street Eyes: pickpocketing, stealth, and scavenging start high; you see what others walk past. Nothing Left to Lose: crime stress halved. The street community shares food and tips.
- The Need: a full addiction with a craving meter, and it is not patient. No Papers: no legal jobs, no bank, no lease until you rebuild your ID. Cops search you on sight in nice neighborhoods.

The hardest life in the game. Getting clean is the greatest run RAGS has."
opening_line = "The Tweaker wakes behind the gas station beside a shopping cart, with every good dumpster already mapped in memory."
